{{> layout/header}}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/information.css">
<main class="cc-main">
    <div class="cc-container cc-info-page">
        <section class="cc-info-hero cc-info-hero--open">
            <div>
                <p class="cc-info-hero__eyebrow">TICKET OPEN CALENDAR</p>
                <h1>오픈 예정</h1>
                <p>놓치고 싶지 않은 공연의 티켓 오픈 일정을 미리 확인하세요.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cc-info-hero__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none"><rect x="10" y="13" width="44" height="41" rx="10"/><path d="M20 8v11M44 8v11M10 25h44"/><path d="m25 39 5 5 11-13"/></svg>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cc-info-section">
            <div class="cc-info-section__head">
                <div>
                    <p class="cc-info-kicker">다가오는 티켓 오픈</p>
                    <h2>이번 주 오픈 일정 <span>6</span></h2>
                </div>
                <div class="cc-info-filter">
                    <button class="is-active" type="button">전체</button>
                    <button type="button">콘서트</button>
                    <button type="button">뮤지컬</button>
                    <button type="button">페스티벌</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cc-schedule-list">
                <article class="cc-card cc-schedule-card cc-schedule-card--today">
                    <div class="cc-schedule-date"><strong>오늘</strong><span>06.01 MON</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-time">19:00</div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-body"><span class="cc-badge cc-badge--fill">단독판매</span><h3>최유리 단독 콘서트 2026</h3><p>일반 예매 · 블루스퀘어 마스터카드홀</p></div>
                    <a class="cc-schedule-link" href="/concerts/11">상세보기 <span>›</span></a>
                </article>
                <article class="cc-card cc-schedule-card cc-schedule-card--today">
                    <div class="cc-schedule-date"><strong>오늘</strong><span>06.01 MON</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-time">20:00</div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-body"><span class="cc-badge">팬클럽 선예매</span><h3>세븐틴 WORLD TOUR &lt;NEW_&gt; IN SEOUL</h3><p>팬클럽 인증 회원 · 고척스카이돔</p></div>
                    <a class="cc-schedule-link" href="/concerts/22">상세보기 <span>›</span></a>
                </article>
                <article class="cc-card cc-schedule-card">
                    <div class="cc-schedule-date"><strong>내일</strong><span>06.02 TUE</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-time">18:00</div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-body"><span class="cc-badge">일반 예매</span><h3>DAY6 4TH WORLD TOUR &lt;FOREVER&gt;</h3><p>일반 예매 · 올림픽공원 KSPO DOME</p></div>
                    <a class="cc-schedule-link" href="/concerts/21">상세보기 <span>›</span></a>
                </article>
                <article class="cc-card cc-schedule-card">
                    <div class="cc-schedule-date"><strong>06.03</strong><span>WED</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-time">14:00</div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-body"><span class="cc-badge">일반 예매</span><h3>10CM 여름 소극장 콘서트</h3><p>일반 예매 · 이화여자대학교 삼성홀</p></div>
                    <a class="cc-schedule-link" href="/concerts/13">상세보기 <span>›</span></a>
                </article>
                <article class="cc-card cc-schedule-card">
                    <div class="cc-schedule-date"><strong>06.04</strong><span>THU</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-time">19:00</div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-body"><span class="cc-badge">단독판매</span><h3>aespa LIVE TOUR &lt;SYNK : HYPER LINE&gt;</h3><p>일반 예매 · 인스파이어 아레나</p></div>
                    <a class="cc-schedule-link" href="/concerts/24">상세보기 <span>›</span></a>
                </article>
                <article class="cc-card cc-schedule-card">
                    <div class="cc-schedule-date"><strong>06.05</strong><span>FRI</span></div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-time">20:00</div>
                    <div class="cc-schedule-body"><span class="cc-badge">일반 예매</span><h3>SUMMER WAVE FESTIVAL 2026</h3><p>얼리버드 티켓 · 난지한강공원</p></div>
                    <a class="cc-schedule-link" href="/concerts/14">상세보기 <span>›</span></a>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>
{{> layout/footer}}
